    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "an5.217:1.1",
          "pli": "“Pañcime, bhikkhave, ādīnavā apāsādike. ",
          "en": "“Mendicants, there are these five drawbacks of uninspiring conduct. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.217:1.2",
          "pli": "Katame pañca? ",
          "en": "What five? "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.217:1.3",
          "pli": "Attāpi attānaṃ upavadati, ",
          "en": "You blame yourself. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.217:1.4",
          "pli": "anuvicca viññū garahanti, ",
          "en": "After examination, sensible people criticize you. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.217:1.5",
          "pli": "pāpako kittisaddo abbhuggacchati, ",
          "en": "You get a bad reputation. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.217:1.6",
          "pli": "sammūḷho kālaṃ karoti, ",
          "en": "You feel lost when you die. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.217:1.7",
          "pli": "kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjati. ",
          "en": "And when your body breaks up, after death, you’re reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.217:1.8",
          "pli": "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca ādīnavā apāsādike. ",
          "en": "These are the five drawbacks of uninspiring conduct. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.217:2.1",
          "pli": "Pañcime, bhikkhave, ānisaṃsā pāsādike. ",
          "en": "There are these five benefits of inspiring conduct. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.217:2.2",
          "pli": "Katame pañca? ",
          "en": "What five? "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.217:2.3",
          "pli": "Attāpi attānaṃ na upavadati, ",
          "en": "You don’t blame yourself. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.217:2.4",
          "pli": "anuvicca viññū pasaṃsanti, ",
          "en": "After examination, sensible people praise you. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.217:2.5",
          "pli": "kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggacchati, ",
          "en": "You get a good reputation. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.217:2.6",
          "pli": "asammūḷho kālaṃ karoti, ",
          "en": "You don’t feel lost when you die. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.217:2.7",
          "pli": "kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjati. ",
          "en": "And when the body breaks up, after death, you’re reborn in a good place, a heavenly realm. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.217:2.8",
          "pli": "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca ānisaṃsā pāsādike”ti. ",
          "en": "These are the five benefits of inspiring conduct.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.217:2.9",
          "pli": "Sattamaṃ. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
